",PCs with the Grimbahack mod,A custom-made arcade stick with new artwork of Lord Drakkon from NWay for 1st place.,,"Winner must keep characters. Loser may switch.
SPD Unblockables Banned (Following applies if you're using the SPD Zord)
- You can't use the M call debuff on an incoming opponent until the opponent's character touches the ground
- You can't swap strike if the opponent's character has an air M call debuff
--- Doing either of these will result in a game loss",,"Thu 1/29, Sun 2/1",,,,,"Under no circumstances should BFTG be scheduled near UMVC3 or 2XKO. Also, whoever is streaming it should be able to handle streaming a 120fps from a PC. We ran into an issue with the streamers from last year, and I want to avoid that scenario again. If there's a need for a change, please let me know.",,,
