Mevious and Memory are not allowed",,,,,,,,,,,"This game potentially needs to be ran as FT1 until finals depending on how skilled the player pool is, me and skytanks thought 2 hours was enough to get through pools for 29 people. We were wrong, we needed 3. That was FT2 for most of the bracket on 4 setups, and only 1 dq. I am keeping it on ft2 for now but that may change.

Since this is a MiSter game, I expect my and other MiSter setups will be shared for other games that need them. I am at least happy to provide mine for whatever is needed

